14 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY 21 O.S. 2021, Section 1111, as
15 last amended by Section 8, Chapter 452, O.S.L. 2024 (21 O.S. Supp.
16 2024, Section 1111), is amended to read as follows:
17 Section 1111. A. Rape is an act of sexual intercourse
18 involving vaginal or anal penetration accomplished with a male or
19 female within or without the bonds of matrimony who may be of the
20 same or the opposite sex as the perpetrator under any of the
21 following circumstances:
22 1. Where the victim is under sixteen (16) eighteen (18) years
23 of age;
